---
layout: base.njk
title: Being Pablo
---

{% set featured = collections.article | homeFeatured %}
{% set featuredUrl = featured.url if featured else "" %}
{% set updates = collections.homeFeed | homeHighlights(featuredUrl, 8) %}

<section class="home-stack home-stack--narrow" aria-labelledby="home-intro-title">
  <section class="home-hero--narrow">
    <header>
      <h1 id="home-intro-title" class="sr-only">Pablo Murad</h1>
      <div class="page-content home-hero-intro">
        <div class="content">
          <p>I am from São Lourenço, Minas Gerais, a small town in southeastern Brazil. Founder of a leading online school in Latin America, and I also work as a software developer.</p>
          <p>Naturally introverted, but always happy to meet new people and build genuine connections. I like staying active in my community and taking part in social projects that can help change lives.</p>
          <p>Developer since 1997, and computers have been one of my lifelong passions.</p>
          <p>You can also see my <em><a href="https://pablo.space/photos">photographs</a></em> and read my <em><a href="https://pablo.space/articles">articles</a></em>.</p>
          <p><em>São Lourenço, Brazil. through strange times</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
       </header>
  </section>

  <section class="home-work home-module" aria-labelledby="home-work-heading">
    <h2 id="home-work-heading" class="home-writing-section-label">Work</h2>
    <ul class="home-work-list" role="list">
      <li class="home-work-row">
        <img class="home-work-icon" src="/assets/pablo/portal-idea.ico" width="32" height="32" alt="" decoding="async">
        <span class="home-work-label">Portal IDEA</span>
      </li>
      <li class="home-work-row">
        <img class="home-work-icon" src="/assets/pablo/grupo-murad.ico" width="32" height="32" alt="" decoding="async">
        <span class="home-work-label">Grupo Murad</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="home-writing home-module" aria-labelledby="home-writing-heading">
    <h2 id="home-writing-heading" class="home-writing-section-label">Recent things with a pulse</h2>
    <ul class="home-writing-list" role="list">
      {% if featured %}
      <li class="home-writing-row home-writing-row--featured">
        <a class="home-writing-row__link" href="{{ featured.url }}">
          <span class="home-writing-type">{{ featured | homeTypeDisplay }}</span>
          <span class="home-writing-row__title">{{ featured | homeTitle }}</span>
        </a>
        <time class="home-writing-date" datetime="{{ featured.date | dateToISO }}">{{ featured.date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { timeZone: 'UTC', month: 'short', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' }) }}</time>
      </li>
      {% endif %}
      {% for post in updates %}
      <li class="home-writing-row">
        <a class="home-writing-row__link" href="{{ post.url }}">
          <span class="home-writing-type">{{ post | homeTypeDisplay }}</span>
          <span class="home-writing-row__title">{{ post | homeTitle }}</span>
        </a>
        <time class="home-writing-date" datetime="{{ post.date | dateToISO }}">{{ post.date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { timeZone: 'UTC', month: 'short', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' }) }}</time>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
</section>
